item.title: How do i change where you start?
item.dc:creator: @0wnz0r 0wnz0r
item.description:
@0wnz0r wrote:

Open up player.java.
Then search for “initial”.
You’ll see something like this:

// initial x and y coordinates of the player heightLevel = 0; // the first call to updateThisPlayerMovement() will craft the proper initialization packet teleportToX = 3281; teleportToY = 3881;

Change the coords.
The numbers: 3281 and 3881.
